sketch.compiler.controlflow

Class CFGBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENullVisitor
      • sketch.compiler.controlflow.CFGBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CFGforPloop

    public class CFGBuilder
extends FENullVisitor
    Helper class to build a control-flow graph from linear code. The buildCFG(sketch.compiler.ast.core.Function) method can be called externally to produce a CFG from a function declaration.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Maze <dmaze@cag.lcs.mit.edu>
